    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. It\u2019s in solid shape with just the usual character you\u2019d expect from a pre-owned car, and it's been super dependable for me. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! Let me know if you want to take it for a spin!",
