    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it. It\u2019s been such a reliable partner for me\u2014super dependable and still has that smooth, comfy ride you're looking for. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready to hit the road for its next chapter with you. If you want a great deal on a car that still has tons of life left in it, come say hi and take it for a test drive!",
