    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and a refreshed suspension setup utilizing Bilstein dampers. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-pressure double-VANOS system operates with precision. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its well-maintained status, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering the tactile feedback and telepathic steering response synonymous with the M-division's peak analog era.",
